Subject: We Appreciate Your Application and Participation

Body:
<html><body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #222222; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Hi <strong>[applicant_first_name]</strong>,</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Thank you for taking the time to participate in the final interview for the <strong>[job_title]</strong> position. We truly appreciate the effort you invested in completing your application and sharing your experience, skills, and insights with us.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">We wanted to take a moment to sincerely thank you for your time and participation throughout the process.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">We encourage you to stay connected - follow us on our social media channels to stay updated on our latest opportunities:</p>
<ul style="margin: 0 0 14px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/OPGteam/">Facebook</a></li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/_opgteam/">Instagram</a></li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">TikTok</li>
<li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/outsourced-pro-global/">LinkedIn</a></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">You're also welcome to refer others who may be a great fit.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">It was a pleasure learning more about you, and we sincerely value your interest in joining Outsourced Pro Global.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 14px 0;">Recruiter contact: [recruiter_phone_line]</p>

[signature]
